e.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="地面控制和噪音 2024 年堕胎福利现在在 Bowery 宴会厅。图片来源：埃米利奥·赫尔塞" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/240120-Ground-Control-Noise-For-Now-Abortion-Benifit-at-Bowery-Ballroom-9-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://groundcontroltouring.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ground Control Touring、</a> <a href="https://noisefornow.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NOISE FOR NOW</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/model-actriz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Model/Actriz</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了第三届年度堕胎福利系列以及唐纳德·特朗普总统就职后社区活动的重要性。</p><p>精品预订机构 Ground Control 与专门从事生殖正义的非营利组织 NOSIE FOR NOW 合作，第三年推出堕胎福利系列——一个旨在筹集资金和提高生殖权利意识的音乐展示活动。</p><p>这些活动将于周六（1 月 25 日）在八个城市举行——洛杉矶、纽约、芝加哥、亚特兰大、费城、奥斯汀、华盛顿特区和罗利——以现场音乐和庆祝活动为特色，例如支持堕胎基金、社区、和身体自主权。所有收益将直接捐献给 NOSIE FOR NOW，然后他们将分配给每个地区的当地独立堕胎诊所和基金。</p><p>今年，该活动将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-trump-on-cusp-of-us-election-victory-entertainment-world-reacts-3809992">特朗普宣誓就职第二任期五天后举行，</a>这使他成为 130 多年来第一位重返总统职位的前总统。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="ht